WHO   — Green — nature · growth
WHAT  — One of the five colours: ramp, the biggest creatures, and unbothered strength, on the conviction that you should accept your role and become strong in it.
WHERE — MTG · MTG Arena  Framework inputs: Magic: The Gathering / MTG Arena (WotC)  Conductor / external anchor: ROOT0 (catalogued into UD0)
